<template>
  <v-app>
    <!-- <moncompte_photo /> -->
     
    <!--<moncompte_info /> -->
    
    <moncompte_modif /> 
     
  </v-app>
</template>

<script>
import axios from "axios";
import moncompte_modif from "@/components/Moncompte_modif";

export default {
  name: "monCompte",
  components: { 
  //  moncompte_photo,
   // moncompte_info,
    moncompte_modif,
  },
  data: () => ({
    idUser: 4,
    user: "", 
  }),
  mounted() {
    console.log("Mounted");
    this.fetchData();
  },
  methods: {
    fetchData() {
      console.log("test start");
      axios
        .get("http://localhost:3000/user/" + this.idUser)
        .then((response) => {
          console.log(response);
        // this.user=response.user
        })
        .catch((error) => {
          console.log(error);
        });
      console.log("test fin");
    },
  },
};
</script>
